description:
The Stuff We Bought From Instagram Ads And LOVE, Mini Ep Edition! For me it’s Baboon to the Moon luggage bags and Sabah shoes. For Jackie it’s Cover Your Assets (the ad was from me), and an Amazon workout set that I also realized I own.


Mentioned On This Episode!

  • Baboon to the Moon Bags: https://fave.co/2SNzfV4
  • Sabah Shoes: https://fave.co/3wHxSoG 
  • Cover Your Assets Game (40% off!): https://amzn.to/3ebmV8j 
  • TikTok Workout Outfit (up to XL which is 18-20): https://amzn.to/3hCQFNH 
  • Plus Size Workout Set (similar to the one above, goes to XXL): https://amzn.to/2VDlOYS 
  • Plus Size Tee Shirt/Leggings Workout Set (Up to 4X): https://amzn.to/3AYCYjN 
  • Athleta’s Size Inclusive Workout Sets: https://fave.co/3wCThiT 
  • Summersalt’s Inclusive Workout Sets (I haven’t tried yet but I want to!): https://fave.co/3eb6A3C
